The paper deals with the task of image captioning, which involves understanding both visual and textual information. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The paper also proposes an unsupervised training approach that incorporates a learning signal from an Image Retrieval model, which involves machine learning techniques. This suggests that the paper may also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
